[ENG]
I was infected by a virus and maybe some of you have received an unusual 
e-mail from me containing an attachment. Delete that mail immediately 
because it contains the virus NetSky.
My computer is safe now. The virus was running in the background with 
process name "FVProtect.exe".
Sorry for this.

[ESP]
Me infecte con un virus y algunos de ustedes por ahi recibieron un mail 
inusual de mi parte conteniendo un attach. Borren el mail inmediatamente 
porque el attach contiene el virus NetSky.
Mi computadora esta limpia ahora. El virus estaba corriendo en 
background con el nombre de proceso "FVProtect.exe".
Perdonde por el inconveniente.


Sebastian.
